3. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with communication systems and transmission of information, which are relevant to networking and internet architecture. 
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses physical-layer design and feedback mechanisms, which are relevant to systems and control. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with transmission of multimedia data over wiretap channels, which is a relevant topic in multimedia.
